  //   Original RESPECT (Carroll JD et al., NEJM 2013;368:1092-1100, PMID 23514286)
  //   DEFENSE-PFO (Lee PH et al., JACC 2018;71:2335-2342, PMID 29544871)
  //
  // These four trials frame the 2017 PFO cluster (CLOSE, REDUCE, RESPECT
  // long-term) by establishing the pre-2017 ambiguity (CLOSURE-I and PC
  // negative; original RESPECT borderline P=0.08 at 2.1y) and the post-2017
  // high-risk-anatomy confirmation (DEFENSE-PFO). Original RESPECT 2013 is
  // a SEPARATE publication from the existing 'respect-trial' entry above,
  // which holds the 2017 long-term extension (Saver JL et al., NEJM 2017).
  // ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

